      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a mechanism for transporting IPv4 packets across an IPv6 network using IP encapsulation.  It also describes a generic mechanism for mapping between IPv6 addresses and IPv4 addresses as well as transport-layer ports.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
